  "text": "Nowadays, the paradigm for type 2 diabetes management has been shifting and insulin is no longer reserved as the last resort, but is increasingly combined with oral antidiabetic drugs at an earlier stage of the physical history of the disease. Few previous RCTs targeted to answer the question if SMBG is lowering A1C in this situation, although adjustment of basal bedtime insulin dosage is based on SMBG readings [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
